  "info": {
    "name": "HT-CentralCashPool-CLM-Mirror-TimeEpoch-BiWeekly-14",
    "_postman_id": "ht-v17-4m-1clm-buyhold",
    "description": "HT v17 — $4M Pool · 1 CLM (Buy-and-Hold only) · useFixedQuantity=true · Bands 20%/25%/30%\n\n  WHAT CHANGED FROM v16:\n  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  Removed: CLM-Lending contract (BTC-CLM-Lending-20)\n  Removed: ADM ad_btc01 (lending ADM)\n  Removed: ADM ad_btc01_mirror (lending mirror)\n\n  Kept: CLM-SpotTrade (buy-and-hold, P1D notice)\n  Kept: ADM ad_btc01_spot + ad_btc01_spot_mirror\n  Kept: CASH-PAM, T-Bills, LiquidityBuffer, all risk factors\n\n  This models a clean Buy-and-Hold BTC position in a CLM:\n    - Capital deployed: $1,000,000 buys 20 BTC @ $50,000 on Mar-01\n    - The BTC is HELD (unencumbered) — can be sold any day (P1D notice)\n    - As price rises, allocation drifts toward the 30% ceiling\n    - When ceiling is breached, ADM sells just enough BTC to return to 25% target\n    - Proceeds flow back to CASH-PAM via the mirror model\n\n  POOL SIZING:\n  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  Constraint: 20 BTC × $50,000 / NAV = 0.25 (target allocation at deployment)\n    NAV = 20 × $50,000 / 0.25 = $4,000,000\n    nonBTC_base = $4,000,000 - $1,000,000 = $3,000,000\n    T-Bills (same ladder) = $988,113\n    Cash residual = $3,000,000 - $988,113 = $2,011,887\n    Pool = $1,000,000 (CLM) + $988,113 (T-Bills) + $2,011,887 (cash) = $4,000,000\n\n  BREACH THRESHOLD:\n  20 × P / (20 × P + 3,000,000) > 0.30  →  P > $64,286\n  First price above this in the path: $65,000 (Apr-15)\n\n  ALLOCATION STORY (1 CLM, 20 BTC, useFixedQuantity=true):\n  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  Feb-28  $49,500   0 BTC    0.0%    CASH-PAM IED. Pool $4M established.\n  Mar-01  $50,000  20 BTC   25.0%   CLM IED: -$1M deployed → 20 BTC. alloc = target ✓\n                                    T-Bill IEDs fire: -$988,113. cash = $2,011,887.\n  Mar-15  $55,000  20 BTC   26.8%   Rising. In band [20%-30%].\n  Mar-31  $60,000  20 BTC   28.6%   Approaching ceiling.\n  Apr-15  $65,000  20 BTC   30.2%   BREACH (> 30% max)\n    → ad_btc01_spot SELL: 3.4615 BTC × $65K = $225,000 returned\n    → ad_btc01_spot_mirror PP +$225,000 on CASH-PAM\n    → Post-sell: 16.5385 BTC × $65K / $4.3M = 25.00% ✓\n  Apr-30  $70,000  16.54 BTC  26.8%   No breach.\n  May-15  $74,000  16.54 BTC  28.7%   Approaching. In band.\n  May-31  $78,000  16.54 BTC  30.1%   BREACH again (> 30% max)\n    → ad_btc01_spot SELL: 2.7885 BTC × $78K = $217,500 returned\n    → ad_btc01_spot_mirror PP +$217,500 on CASH-PAM\n    → Post-sell: 13.75 BTC × $78K / $4.29M = 25.00% ✓\n  Jun-01  $75,000  13.75 BTC   —      TBILL-3mo-400K matures → +$400,000\n  Jun-30  $90,000  13.75 BTC  29.2%   Near ceiling but no breach.\n  Jul-01  $89,000  13.75 BTC   —      TBILL-4mo-350K matures → +$350,000\n  Aug-01  $77,000  13.75 BTC   —      TBILL-5mo-250K matures → +$250,000\n  Aug-31  $65,000  13.75 BTC  23.0%   All contracts settle. Pool winds down.\n\n  SCENARIO: ht_v17_4m_1clm_buyhold_scn01   STEPS: 9   CONTRACTS: 5",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
